How Chaining Works in This Example

Propagation: task_tech.context=[task_fin] passes financial JSON (e.g., EBITDA) as input context.
Parallelism: Tech & ESG run concurrently after Fin (CrewAI handles via async delegation).
Conditionals: In task_risk, agent prompt checks HHI threshold; if high, adds escalation (LLM decides based on context).
Memory: Crew's memory=True retains full chain state for later tasks.
Tracing: verbose=2 logs: "Financial Agent passing to Tech: {output}".

